---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Pour Your Own Candle Class"
  description="Create beautiful hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents. Perfect for beginners in Centerville, TN."
  price="$20-30 per person"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="pour your own candle, hand-poured candles, candle class, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Pour Your Own Candle Class - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>
      Enjoy the satisfaction of creating your own beautiful hand-poured candles in our popular Pour Your Own Candle Class. This hands-on experience is perfect for beginners and allows you to customize colors, fragrances, and container styles to match your preferences.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      You'll pour premium soy wax into beautiful containers while our instructors guide you through proper temperature control, pouring techniques, and fragrance blending. Watch as your liquid wax transforms into stunning candles that are ready to use immediately or take home to enjoy.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Expert instruction throughout the pouring process</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax and fragrances</li>
      <li>Choice of beautiful containers</li>
      <li>Color customization options</li>
      <li>Fragrance selection from 40+ scents</li>
      <li>All supplies and materials</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 beautiful candles</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Date nights, solo creative time, group celebrations, or anyone who loves candles and crafting. No experience necessary—all skill levels welcome.
    </p>

    <h3>Why Choose Made @ The Local Pottery and Candle Studio</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Expert candle makers provide hands-on guidance</li>
      <li>Premium materials ensure beautiful results</li>
      <li>Wide fragrance selection for customization</li>
      <li>Relaxed, creative atmosphere</li>
      <li>Perfect location for a destination experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and safety briefing (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Select your fragrance, color, and container (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Hands-on pouring with guidance (45-60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and cooling (20 minutes)</li>
      <li>Wrap and take home your creations!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $20-30 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-8 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Ready to pour?</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com to book. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"This was so much fun! I made beautiful candles and the staff was incredibly helpful. Absolutely worth the drive from Nashville!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Michelle L.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect date activity. We made matching candles and had such a great time together. The café afterwards was a nice bonus!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>David & Amanda</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Took my mom here and she loved it. Easy to follow, fun to do, and the results are beautiful. Highly recommend!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Kyle M.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Candle Making Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional candle-making techniques from start to finish.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/candle-making-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Scented Candle Making Experience</h3>
        <p>Blend your own signature scents and create custom scented candles.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/scented-candle-making-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Container Candle Making</h3>
        <p>Pour and design candles in beautiful containers to take home immediately.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/container-candle-making" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
